<L>__{interior board room, paramount studios day}
<A>__{now barney balaban is reading hitchcock's publicity manual to the board.}
<C>__{barney balaban}
<D>__{"absolutely never, ever will i allow anything to follow psycho no previews of coming attractions, no newsreel, no short subject and certainly no double feature. sincerely, and, emphatically, alfred hitchcock."}
<A>__{balaban shuts the pamphlet. silence. then turns to the stone faced board members :}
<C>__{barney balaban }
<D>__{at the end of the day, it's a minor hitchcock movie. one week, and it'll be gone...}
<A>__{he tosses the pamphlet into the trash.}
<C>__{barney balaban }
<D>__{like a bad dream. 138 }
